background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"5733513711 8b238fd116 z b0wyi7\"\n        title=\"Imagining Anish Kapoor´s Leviathan - (cc) Alexandre Marchand\"\n        src=\"/static/5733513711_8b238fd116_z_b0wyi7-9ccf9afee59cc4871f09746095eea6d7-82f60.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5733513711_8b238fd116_z_b0wyi7-9ccf9afee59cc4871f09746095eea6d7-0c02d.jpg 200w,\n/static/5733513711_8b238fd116_z_b0wyi7-9ccf9afee59cc4871f09746095eea6d7-84cac.jpg 400w,\n/static/5733513711_8b238fd116_z_b0wyi7-9ccf9afee59cc4871f09746095eea6d7-82f60.jpg 431w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 431px) 100vw, 431px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    \n  <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Imagining Anish Kapoor´s Leviathan - (cc) Alexandre Marchand</figcaption>\n  </figure>\n      </p>\n<p>\n  <figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n  \n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5734062310_f1b8744621_z_l0l6xp-f503b6d3b2e9067674d1cd072081d989-82f60.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; null; max-width: 431px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 148.49187935034803%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"5734062310 f1b8744621 z l0l6xp\"\n        title=\"Imagining Anish Kapoor´s Leviathan - (cc) Alexandre Marchand\"\n        src=\"/static/5734062310_f1b8744621_z_l0l6xp-f503b6d3b2e9067674d1cd072081d989-82f60.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5734062310_f1b8744621_z_l0l6xp-f503b6d3b2e9067674d1cd072081d989-0c02d.jpg 200w,\n/static/5734062310_f1b8744621_z_l0l6xp-f503b6d3b2e9067674d1cd072081d989-84cac.jpg 400w,\n/static/5734062310_f1b8744621_z_l0l6xp-f503b6d3b2e9067674d1cd072081d989-82f60.jpg 431w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 431px) 100vw, 431px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    \n  <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Imagining Anish Kapoor´s Leviathan - (cc) Alexandre Marchand</figcaption>\n  </figure>\n      </p>\n<p>\n  <figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n  \n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5734064082_23e72d421b_z_vanhwf-a6094844145d919257f72ed39625ff45-55fd7.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; null; max-width: 640px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 67.34375%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"5734064082 23e72d421b z vanhwf\"\n        title=\"Imagining Anish Kapoor´s Leviathan - (cc) Alexandre Marchand\"\n        src=\"/static/5734064082_23e72d421b_z_vanhwf-a6094844145d919257f72ed39625ff45-55fd7.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5734064082_23e72d421b_z_vanhwf-a6094844145d919257f72ed39625ff45-e81c0.jpg 200w,\n/static/5734064082_23e72d421b_z_vanhwf-a6094844145d919257f72ed39625ff45-8e8ea.jpg 400w,\n/static/5734064082_23e72d421b_z_vanhwf-a6094844145d919257f72ed39625ff45-55fd7.jpg 640w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    \n  <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Imagining Anish Kapoor´s Leviathan - (cc) Alexandre Marchand</figcaption>\n  </figure>\n      </p>\n<p>In one of his interviews, Anish Kapoor explains the significance of this project. He says he wants the viewer to “have a moment of a shock, aesthetically but also physically so that when you enter you would go wow.” Colour, he says, played a big role in this piece and his objective was to make it an all-encompassing monochrome. He also wants the viewer to bring both their body and memory in the act of looking at this piece.</p>\n<div>\n          <div\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-iframe-wrapper\"\n            style=\"padding-bottom: 78.90625%; position: relative; height: 0; overflow: hidden;margin-bottom: 2em\"\n          >\n            <iframe allowfullscreen class=\"youtube-player\" frameborder=\"0\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/rt3ZcMO8JFI?wmode=transparent&amp;fs=1&amp;hl=en&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;iv_load_policy=3&amp;showsearch=0&amp;rel=0&amp;theme=dark\" title=\"YouTube video player\" type=\"text/html\" style=\"\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n          \"></iframe>\n          </div>\n          </div>\n<figcaption>Anish Kapoor Interview</figcaption>\n<div>\n          <div\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-iframe-wrapper\"\n            style=\"padding-bottom: 78.90625%; position: relative; height: 0; overflow: hidden;margin-bottom: 2em\"\n          >\n            <iframe allowfullscreen class=\"youtube-player\" frameborder=\"0\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/F6QJ4V3Z_h8?wmode=transparent&amp;fs=1&amp;hl=en&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;iv_load_policy=3&amp;showsearch=0&amp;rel=0&amp;theme=dark&amp;feature=related\" title=\"YouTube video player\" type=\"text/html\" style=\"\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n          \"></iframe>\n          </div>\n          </div>\n<figcaption>Anish Kapoor Interview</figcaption>\n<p><em>All Photos in the Gallery by Alexandre Marchand</em></p>","fields":{"slug":"/imagining-anish-kapoors-leviathan/","prefix":"21 May 2011"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Imagining Being Inside the Belly of a Whale in Anish Kapoor´s Leviathan","category":"artists","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/anishkapoor2_hu074d-d7e2b85a3471b19311efa0efdcd013ef-d927d.jpg"}}}}},"authornote":{"id":"6b2c6198-d5e1-5353-bb7b-a0bc41999229","html":"<p>Article by <strong>Tuesday Gutierrez</strong>. Former digital marketing manager for the London 2012 Festival, the largest UK festival ever staged. This is her blog about contemporary art, design, film, photography and all that move her soul.</p>"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/imagining-anish-kapoors-leviathan/","prev":{"id":"76ea3f72-8f24-52ec-900e-8ff3270f1e2c","fields":{"slug":"/the-hunger-of-joan-miro-tate-modern-2011/","prefix":"14 May 2011","source":"posts"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Starving Myself with Joan Miró´s Retrospective at the Tate Modern","category":"exhibits"}},"next":{"id":"1c1b94b7-0b80-518e-bdc0-733b85008b0b","fields":{"slug":"/street-art-show-bonanza-this-june-banksy-basquiat-le-rat-at-the-opera-gallery/","prefix":"25 May 2011","source":"posts"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Why I will not Miss This Street Art Show Bonanza: Banksy, Basquiat, Le Rat at the Opera Gallery","category":"exhibits"}},"source":"posts"}}